This is the FreeBSD port of Chromium, corresponding to ports svn revision 325515.

You will need to put llvm-file-map and llvm-link-wrapper in your path and also update the paths in chromium-courgette-redacted-29.0.1547.57/out/Release/build.ninja to reflect your setup

To build the bitcode version of chrome (chrome.bc), cd into chromium-courgette-redacted-29.0.1547.57/out/Release and type:
$ ninja chrome.soaap

To build an executable from chrome.bc, type:
$ ninja chrome.bc.exe
